  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Omnibus collecting the second half of Uriel Ventris's pre-Primaris career: The Killing Ground (Salinas, Governor Barbaden's massacre, the Unfleshed pursuing Uriel out of the Eye of Terror); Courage and Honour (the Tau Empire's invasion of Pavonis under Shas'O Or'es'ka'an and Aun'rai, defended by the 4th Company plus Lord Winterbourne's Imperial Guard regiment); and The Chapter's Due (Honsou's Skull Harvest revenge invasion of Ultramar, with Iron Warriors and the Khornate Bloodborn assaulting Calth at sector scale). The arc moves from one Astartes's character-study and death-oath investigation to a chapter-scale war for survival. Not the canonical series entry-point — that is The Ultramarines Omnibus / Uriel Ventris Chronicles Vol. 1, which collects books 1–3 — but the natural follow-on volume for readers continuing the saga.",
